data.description: ONE OF A KIND OPPORTUNITY! ENERGY INDEPENDENCE! $2000 credit to Buyer upon accepted offer. Custom built 2BR possible 3BR. OWNED Photo Voltaic/ Solar Panels. MINIMAL electric bill or conventional power. Home is situated on 2.5 acres w/majestic VIEWS and clear skies ONLY 5 minutes from I-25, schools and shopping and 22 minutes to downtown Albuq. Open floor plan Includes: Beautiful kitchen w/bfst bar,SS appliances, a cozy open living area, wood stove, large windows to enjoy the views and passive solar, primary bath has a garden tub and custom tile surround shower, REFRIGERATED AIR, Radiant Heat, Pipe fenced lot w/3 separate access pts, great for HORSES, a gravity fed irrigation system w/storage tank and separate orchard area. Don't miss this home!
